Coastal Ice Cream Shop Watercolor Postcard – 4th Of July Invitations Coastal Ice Cream Shop Watercolor Postcard Have a promotion during this period Coastal Ice Cream Shop Watercolor Postcard order now with fast delivery service to your hand as soon as possibleSend someone a special note with this Independence Day themed postcard featuring an original watercolor painting of a quaint, New England ice cream stand. Rocket’s Ice Cream Shop, features a cute, coastal Maine ice cream window where you can order all of your favorite flavors, take in the beautiful view, or even buy some firework bottle rockets to celebrate the season. A quiet scene, this weathered storefront is closed now, but the lobster boats and mallard ducks and ducklings are up early to beat the crowd. A truly unique card for the summer or 4th of July holiday, this little bit of mail was created as the July page of a calendar and doubles as frameable artwork. Blank on the inside for writing a note to friends and family. Price:$2.05
